The paper deals with the design of control systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of symbolic models and automata-based specifications suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of logic in computer science (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper's focus on networked control systems suggests that it may also be relevant to the sub-categories of robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
